{"lemma":"أَحْمَدانِ","slug":"أَحْمَدانِ","root":"ح.م.د","root_slug":"ح-م-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-م-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَحْمَد","root":"حمد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9034"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9034","headword_ar":"احمد","root":"Hmd","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came to a state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result, such as was praised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approved;"},{"kind":"text","text":"properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, came to such a state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"result:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K:) or (so in the K, but in the L “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"said, that for which he should be praised,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commended;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which was praiseworthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commendable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L, K; *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*am~a","text_ar":"اَذَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmd A^amoruhu","text_ar":"احمد اَمْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, praiseworthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approvable, in his estimation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmd A^amorahu","text_ar":"احمد اَمْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as in the L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he esteemed his affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, praiseworthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approvable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L [agreeably with what next follows].)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmdhu","text_ar":"احمدهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, A, L) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be such as is praised, commended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approved;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"praiseworthy, commendable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approvable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, L, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*am~ahu","text_ar":"اَذَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*m","text_ar":"ذم"},{"kind":"text","text":":)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made it manifest that he was worthy of praise, eulogy, commendation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approbation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he approved of his action,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his course of conduct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his tenet"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tenets, and did not expose it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"them, to others."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomadotu SaniyEahu","text_ar":"اَحْمَدْتُ صَنِيعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found his action to be praiseworthy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"commendable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approvable"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmd AlA^aroDa","text_ar":"احمد الاَرْضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He approved the land as a dwelling-place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he found the land to be such as is praised, commended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approved;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamidahaA","text_ar":"حَمِدَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K;) but the former verb is the more chaste in this sense. (L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHmd mawoDiEFA","text_ar":"احمد مَوْضِعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He found a place to be such as is praised, commended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approved, and convenient,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suitable, so that he approved it as a dwelling-place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for its pasture."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","K","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%A3%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF/","headword_ar":"أحمد","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_27","lexicon_en":"Al-Barakatī, al-Taʿrīfāt al-Fiqhīya (d. 1975 CE)","lexicon_ar":"التعريفات الفقهيّة للبركتي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=46483#5154b5","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">أحمد</span><span>: صَلَّى الله عليه وسَلَّم- هو اسم نبينا ورسولنا سيدنا ومولانا محمدٍ خاتمِ النبيين- صلى الله عليه وسلم- معناه: الفاضل عمن عداه في الحامدية يعني ليس غيره كثير الحمد لله تعالى، لأنه عليه السلام عريف له تعالى. وقلة الحمد وكثرته بحسب قلة المعرفة وكثرتها، أو معناه كثير المحمودية بلسان الأولين والآخرين. قال الراغب في \"المفردات\": \"وخص لفظة أحمد فيما بشَّر به عيسى عليه السلام تنبيهاً على أنه صلى الله عليه وسلم أحمد منه ومن الذين قبله.<br><div>وقوله تعالى: {مُحَمَّدٌ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ} [الفتح:29] فمحمد ههنا وإن كان وجهٍ اسماً له عَلَماً ففيه إشارةٌ إلى وصفه بذلك وتخصيصه بمعناه، وقال: \"يقال فلانٌ محمود إذا حُمد، ومحمَّد إذا كثرت خصالة المحمودة، ومحمَّد إذا وُجد محموداً\".</div><div>فهو صلى الله عليه وسلم محمودٌ في ذاته وصفاته وأخلاقه وجميع خصاله وأحواله.</div></span>"}]}}